HEADWORD: Stolid
<hw>Stol"id</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stolidus</ets>.]</ety> <def>Hopelessly insensible or stupid; not
easily aroused or excited; dull; impassive; foolish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stolidity</ent>⟦br⟧
